{
  "texts": [
    "However, their focus is on general object detection.",
    "In comparison, our survey not only introduces general object detection but also provides detailed insights into object detection approaches for various tasks within traffic scenarios.",
    "There have also been recent reviews specifically focused on different traffic scene tasks.",
    "Ning, Menglu, Hao, Xueping, and Yunhong [12] Primarily concentrate on pedestrian object detection, Wali, Abdullah, Hannan, Hussain, Samad, Ker, and Mansor [13] focus on traffic sign detection, Maity, Banerjee, and Chaudhuri [14] emphasize vehicle object detection.",
    "We conduct in-depth assessments from these various angles, comprehensively reviewing existing deep learning-based object detection methods in traffic scenes."
  ]
}